\f1\b 'SavingsAccount'
\f2\b0  prints "Adding 5% interest to balance" and 
\f1\b 'CurrentAccount'
\f2\b0  prints "No interest applied (Standard checking)".\
\ls2\ilvl0\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 d) Create a static method 
